{"id":"3f47d77d-df85-45d5-ba99-6dad1fff1997","name":"PeanutButter","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(11, 69, 255)\">Cuddle time with PeanutButter.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(11, 69, 255)\">Artist: theycallhimcake</span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/71b426f3-aace-41a3-b26f-f91a9c880597_f0fbc1d0-bc56-45bb-816e-1c11ea9b2970.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 11, 255)\">[NOTE: As much as I admire Cake as a person and the dedication he puts in his art, I'm afraid that I'll have to pass on the merchandise he now has on sale. I heard he's got the body pillow case of PB up on sale, though I can't get it otherwise my relatives would question my habits. I know I've been very secretive about this for a long time but I want to make sure it's out there. I love theycallhimcake for what he does and as a person. The streams, the art, Palm Plaza Mall... Everything. He seems like a nice guy and I'd love to join his streams someday. I really do like him. Deeply... Yet I've been so hush hush about it. I've tried to get judgment from an outside perspective for weeks but never got a chance. I still love you guys too. I appreciate the support I've gotten on some platforms, even if I'm not famous which is fine. At the end of day, I'm just another guy who loves Vtubers and Vaporwave, just like theycallhimcake.]</span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 416px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/71b426f3-aace-41a3-b26f-f91a9c880597_363aac53-31ca-4712-96a6-e960ee438b14.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 418px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/71b426f3-aace-41a3-b26f-f91a9c880597_4eaf1224-7961-423c-9114-a4a25f3a5d98.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 421px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janito